---
title: Maple-Mustard Roasted Chicken With Herbed Wild Rice and Buttery Veg Trio
description: This chicken dinner benefits from having the power flavor combo of maple and mustard at the helm. Herb-laced wild rice and a slick side of glazed carrots, radishes and snap peas round out this familiar and comforting meal.
